    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1952-04-14T18:40:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1952-04-14T18:40:00-05:00" n="690"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d690">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">357.AB/4–1452: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The United States Representative at the United Nations</hi>
                        (<persName corresp="#p_AWR1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Austin</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Department of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New York</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1952-04-14T18:40:00-05:00"
                            >April 14, 1952—6:40 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>705. Re Kashmir. <gloss target="#t_reDeptel1">Re Deptel</gloss> 388,<note n="1"
                        xml:id="d690fn1">
                        <ref target="#d689">
                            <hi rend="italic">Supra</hi>
                        </ref>.</note> UKDel has received report from <gloss target="#t_UKHC1"
                        >UKHC</gloss> Karachi similar to that contained in Karachi’s 1178 and
                    instructions from <gloss target="#t_FonOff1">FonOff</gloss> to talk to <persName
                        corresp="#p_GDF1">Graham</persName> along lines similar to those suggested
                    in <gloss target="#t_Deptel1">Deptel</gloss> 388. UKDel also had report on
                        <persName corresp="#p_BCB1">Bowles</persName>–<persName corresp="#p_BSGS1"
                        >Bajpai</persName> conversation (New Delhi 3732).<note n="2"
                        xml:id="d690fn2">Dated Apr. 11, <ref target="#pg_1225">p. 1225</ref>.</note>
                    Since Jebb had date to see <persName corresp="#p_GDF1">Graham</persName> at noon
                    today, <gloss target="#t_USUN1">USUN</gloss> felt it unnecessary for us to
                    convey similar information and views separately to <persName corresp="#p_GDF1"
                        >Graham</persName>.</p>
                <p>. . . . . . .</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_AWR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Austin</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
